{"tid":681220,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【吉林地震】寧江區凌晨5.7級地震 東北多地震感強烈","createTime":"2018-05-28T00:25:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-28T03:19:04.000Z","uid":65346,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8d10f5275ddd499dec38b2d755a6e41adf1a334a","tid":681220,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T00:25:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180528/58245744\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180528%2F58245744&d=P4z59FLyJTqyFyH6MyYIsG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=c74ef30b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180528%2F58245744&h=5e88ff17\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180528/58245744</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n中國吉林省松原市寧江區凌晨1時50分發生<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">5.7級</span>地震，震源深度13公里。吉林和黑龍江多個縣市震感強烈，有市民上街避難，部份房屋出現牆壁開裂，玻璃破損的情況。據地震災害快速評估結果，可能有人員傷亡，造成千餘間房屋受損，中國地震局決定啟動三級地震應急回應。<br />\n不過，央視隨後報道指，經初步調查，暫無人員傷亡報告，個別房屋輕微裂痕，有民房的煙囪掉落、院牆坍塌。新華社記者則指，從松原市委宣傳部獲悉，當地已啟動應急預案，目前尚未有人員傷亡報告。一些群眾表示，松原城區震感強烈，不少市民在地震發生後陸續來到街道上。目前，當地電力供應正常，但部份流動通訊網路連接困難。<br />\n另有報道指，中國地震台網指，據移動人口大數據分析，本次地震震中20公里範圍內人口數約123萬，50公里範圍內約207萬，100公里範圍內約391萬。<br />\n中國鐵路哈爾濱局集團有限公司採取緊急措施，對京哈線、濱洲線、濱綏線等既有線運行的85趟客貨運列車採取就近扣停措施。經檢查、確認線路未受影響後，扣停列車已全部恢復運行，運輸秩序未受影響。"},{"pid":"77319b965db76c11eacc26bd065a61e78bfc86cd","tid":681220,"uid":54337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T00:26:01.000Z","msg":"無事。又贏"},{"pid":"24343de4293cf46c52c323ee1f54c948f9d8d554","tid":681220,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T00:27:06.000Z","msg":"香港樓市大下跌"},{"pid":"37840385a1722e49b8e416d3e13056cb8516d33b","tid":681220,"uid":18867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T00:51:34.000Z","msg":"曾經有人話今年中國會有大地震 唔通係先兆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66651c7f6eaa4da0bbb5fd564f754247b533bd08","tid":681220,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37840385a1722e49b8e416d3e13056cb8516d33b","tid":681220,"uid":18867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T00:51:34.000Z","msg":"曾經有人話今年中國會有大地震 唔通係先兆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T01:02:10.000Z","msg":"全球同步.....<br />\n可能係最大一次地殼變動..香港已死"},{"pid":"fe147c1821562d2ee85b52125649f583ca83a604","tid":681220,"uid":71657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T01:04:26.000Z","msg":"5.7級地震無人傷亡？中國喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e89b3334241e0c4a08087fd8366b8eaab729339","tid":681220,"uid":65346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fe147c1821562d2ee85b52125649f583ca83a604","tid":681220,"uid":71657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T01:04:26.000Z","msg":"5.7級地震無人傷亡？中國喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T01:05:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c38900a1a443b53f21dfef361b45ffb06b61bf4","tid":681220,"uid":74399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe147c1821562d2ee85b52125649f583ca83a604","tid":681220,"uid":71657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T01:04:26.000Z","msg":"5.7級地震無人傷亡？中國喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T01:37:32.000Z","msg":"未有傷亡報告嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc3677b027c043eaaf6cc1ed3caafe0b73e96523","tid":681220,"uid":84081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T02:44:15.000Z","msg":"多難興邦 泥水股gogogo"},{"pid":"c218e98f6957eefb2bcf6cdcc93b792d3df2ac49","tid":681220,"uid":86893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T03:01:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d41f3461dff35f2d3c4f5dc0813110a35ffe23bc","tid":681220,"uid":166785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T03:12:58.000Z","msg":"贏國又贏"},{"pid":"b15227c4bc8673d18e04260595d9ae54c19ef0ad","tid":681220,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T03:19:04.000Z","msg":"5.7 , 香港人鄉下(日本) 濕濕碎啦"}]}